### 1. Test Welcome Message
GET http://localhost:8080/welcome

### 2. Add a Book (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/addbook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "1",
  "title": "Spring Boot in Action",
  "author": "Craig Walls",
  "price": 29.99
}

### 3. Add Another Book (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/addbook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "2",
  "title": "Effective Java",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "price": 45.00
}

### 4. View All Books (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/viewbooks

### 5. Get Book Titles (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/books

### 6. Get Book by ID (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/1

### 7. Search Book by Title (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/search?title=Spring Boot in Action

### 8. Get Author Profile (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/author/Craig Walls

### 9. Get Book Count (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/count

### 10. Get Static Price (GET)
    GET http://localhost:8080/price

